articles.author: Stefan Sykes
articles.title: 'Taylor Swift: The Eras Tour’ concert film set for global theatrical release - CNBC
articles.description: Taylor Swift's highly anticipated The Eras Tour concert film will expand beyond North America for a worldwide premiere date next month.
articles.content:
Taylor Swift's highly anticipated concert film is getting a global release.
The pop superstar's upcoming movie, which chronicles her record-breaking and economy-boosting The Eras Tour, was slated to… [+1770 chars]
